::KitKat::

Her body trembled as he picked her up.  She whimpered at the pain in 
her ribs when he lifted her up. Her legs where pretty well banged 
up.  She was covered in scraped and cuts.  She lifted her head 
slightly and looked at Atma. "Forgive me, what was your question?"

She was having trouble breathing.  Her chest hurt with every breath. 
She gasped a few times and caughed real hard.  She growled at the 
pain running through her body.  She closed her eyes for a few moments 
tto at wonder how the Matrix seamed to have it in for her lately.
